# Eclipse Mosquitto ACL Configuration for SwimEx EDGE
# =====================================================
# Pattern substitution: %u = username, %c = clientID

# Edge server has full access to all swimex topics
user edge-server
topic readwrite swimex/#
topic readwrite $SYS/#

# PLC controllers can publish status and subscribe to commands
user plc-controller
topic readwrite swimex/+/status/#
topic readwrite swimex/+/command/#
topic readwrite swimex/+/keepalive

# Edge clients (tablets) get read access to status, write to commands
user edge-client
topic read swimex/+/status/#
topic write swimex/+/command/#
topic readwrite swimex/+/keepalive

# External SCADA/BMS read-only access to status
user scada-client
topic read swimex/+/status/#

# Default: deny all not explicitly allowed
